Har du husket at lægge resten af filerne i c: programmer TBOOKS?
Avast Antivirus found a Junkie-XXXX Virus in the .BAS files.

@LinuxxxUser:
True.
AVG reports junkie in the .bas - files too.
But:
Junkie is an old DOS-virus tha propagates via executable files (.com, .exe).
The .bas-files are not executables, they contain the dictionary databases.
I'd say that the real risk of infection is very low.
Jugde for yourself. 
:-)
